ond seltzer water the kashering of cocacola american jewish historical society retrieved february     fleemans pharmacy now the belly general store   jack fleeman –  – owner atlanta journalconstitution georgia august     coke can history archived from the original on january     new coke – top  bad beverage ideas timecom april     rory carroll in baghdad july   cola wars as coke moves on baghdad the guardian london retrieved march     according to a cocacola customerservice representative  a b mckay betsy january   coke to omit classic the wall street journal   klinemann jeffrey january   pepsico’s in the club… store that is capturing costco food service account bevnet retrieved april     fredrix emily and sarah skidmore november   costco nixes coke products over pricing dispute associated press archived from the original on november     coke cuts price on mini cans to lure shoppers asheville citizentimes associated press september   retrieved september   dead link  cocacola returns to burma after a year absence bbc news june     jordan tony june   cocacola announces will return to myanmar after  years bloomberg   calderon justin june   cocacola starts bottling in myanmar inside investor retrieved june     coca cola to invest rs  cr in india june     geller martinne june   coke to sell natural midcalorie cola in argentina reuters retrieved june     beverages giant cocacola acquires pc stake in monster for bn pittsburgh newsnet august   retrieved august     jarvis paul december   cocacola buys ab inbev out of africa unit for  billion bloomberg news bloomberg retrieved february   cocacola co will pay  billion to buy anheuserbusch inbev nv out of an african bottling joint venture  cocacola also agreed to buy ab inbev’s interest in bottling operations in zambia zimbabwe botswana swaziland lesotho el salvador and honduras for an undisclosed sum   home of cocacola uk  diet coke  coke zero – cocacola gb letsgettogethercouk april   archived from the original on may   retrie